{"tid":1564648,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"勇武 marking scheme","createTime":"2019-09-13T00:37:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T04:10:35.000Z","uid":283494,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"605c754bd4d7e6a84c9996bd1c9514505531a6ba","tid":1564648,"uid":283494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T00:37:31.000Z","msg":"唔知大家的朋友, 喺勇武呢一科,考到幾多分?<br />\n<br />\n喺過去三個多月, 以下每中一個point加一分。<br />\n<br />\n出席民陣遊行或集會<br />\n出席民陣遊行或集會五次<br />\n叫喊香港人加油<br />\n叫喊光復香港時代革命<br />\n製作路障或在地上淋油或撒棋子或同級<br />\n起地磚<br />\n擲地磚或同級<br />\n運送物資往前線<br />\n資助小朋友或捐款到星火或同類組織<br />\n弄熄交通燈<br />\n拆国旗或区旗<br />\n協助推低智慧燈柱<br />\n港鐵跳閘<br />\n港鐵爆閘機或同級<br />\n製作連儂牆<br />\n阻止別人破壞連儂牆<br />\n包圍加問候乞人憎人士<br />\n捉住乞人旬人士<br />\n動手教訓乞人憎人士<br />\n對警察使用鐳射筆<br />\n燒雜物<br />\n製作燃燒彈或同級<br />\n擲燃燒彈或同級<br />\n處理催淚彈<br />\n問候警察<br />\n包圍警署<br />\n於街上用噴柒<br />\n在標誌建築物用噴柒<br />\n幫手拉回被警察捉住的手足<br />\n用棍或同級與警察短兵相接<br />\n<br />\n評分:<br />\n<br />\n&gt;=25分 - 5**<br />\n21-24分 - 5*<br />\n17-20分 - 5<br />\n12-16分 - 4<br />\n8-11分 - 3<br />\n4-7分 - 2<br />\n1-3分 - 1<br />\n<br />\n大家既朋友攞幾分?"},{"pid":"1f24d479da85228ecf71a6574c303c869b4a146f","tid":1564648,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T00:37:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" />